author: julianfoad
msg: On the 'move-tracking-2' branch: In 'svnmover' let the default log message be
the list of commands instead of an empty message, for easier debugging.
* subversion/svnmover/svnmover.h
(svnmover_wc_t): Add a new field to accumulate the log message.
* subversion/svnmover/svnmoverc
(wc_commit): If no log msg provided, use the list of commands.
(action_t): Add a new field to accumulate the list of commands for this
action.
(execute): Add each command to the list after successfully executing it.
(parse_actions): Store the original words as well as parsing them.
(sub_main): Make the default log message null rather than empty.
